#: ../../source/tutorials/models/PaddleOCR-VL.md:103
msgid ""
"PaddleOCR-VL supports single-node single-card deployment on the A2 series"
" and Atlas 300 inference products platform. Single-node deployment "
"completes both Prefill and Decode within the same node."
msgstr "PaddleOCR-VL 支持在 A2 系列和 Atlas 300 推理产品平台上进行单节点单卡部署。单节点部署在同一节点内完成 Prefill 和 Decode。"

