"ModelScope."
msgstr "准备模型权重：确保模型权重可访问。设置 `VLLM_USE_MODELSCOPE=True` 后，模型将从 ModelScope 自动加载。"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/PaddleOCR-VL.md:108
