"Set the `MODEL_PATH` environment variable to point to your model "
"directory."
msgstr "设置 `MODEL_PATH` 环境变量指向模型目录。"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/PaddleOCR-VL.md:109
msgid "Create and execute the deployment script (save as `deploy.sh`)."
msgstr "创建并执行部署脚本（保存为 `deploy.sh`）。"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/PaddleOCR-VL.md:111
msgid "Startup Command:"
msgstr "启动命令："

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/PaddleOCR-VL.md:166
msgid "On Atlas 300 inference products:"
msgstr "在 Atlas 300 推理产品上："

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/PaddleOCR-VL.md:168
msgid "Only `float16` dtype is supported."
msgstr "仅支持 `float16` 数据类型。"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/PaddleOCR-VL.md:169
msgid ""
"The `--max_model_len` option is added to prevent errors when generating "
"the attention operator mask."
msgstr "添加 `--max_model_len` 选项是为了防止生成注意力算子掩码时出错。"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/PaddleOCR-VL.md:170
msgid ""
"Graph compilation (`--compilation-config`) requires **CANN version >= "
"9.0.0**. If your CANN version is lower, please revert to eager mode by "
"replacing the `--compilation-config` argument with `--enforce-eager`."
msgstr "图编译（`--compilation-config`）需要 **CANN 版本 >= 9.0.0**。如果 CANN 版本较低，请将 `--compilation-config` 参数替换为 `--enforce-eager` 以回退到 eager 模式。"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/PaddleOCR-VL.md:171
msgid ""
"The `fuse_norm_quant` option in `--additional_config` is disabled "
"(`false`) because it is not supported by the graph compilation on this "
"hardware. Keep this setting unchanged."
msgstr "`--additional_config` 中的 `fuse_norm_quant` 选项已禁用（`false`），因为该硬件的图编译不支持此功能。请保持此设置不变。"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/PaddleOCR-VL.md:174
msgid "Key Parameter Descriptions:"
msgstr "关键参数说明："

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/PaddleOCR-VL.md:176
msgid ""
"`--max-num-batched-tokens` specifies the maximum number of tokens batched"
" in a single forward pass. Adjust this parameter for throughput "
"optimization."
msgstr "`--max-num-batched-tokens` 指定单次前向传播中批处理的最大 token 数量。调整此参数以优化吞吐量。"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/PaddleOCR-VL.md:177
msgid ""
"`--max_model_len` specifies the maximum context length — that is, the sum"
" of input and output tokens for a single request."
msgstr "`--max_model_len` 指定最大上下文长度，即单个请求的输入和输出 token 之和。"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/PaddleOCR-VL.md:178
msgid ""
"`--no-enable-prefix-caching` indicates that prefix caching is disabled. "
"To enable it, remove this option."
msgstr "`--no-enable-prefix-caching` 表示禁用前缀缓存。要启用它，请移除该选项。"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/PaddleOCR-VL.md:179
msgid ""
"`--mm-processor-cache-gb` sets the size of the multimodal processor cache"
" (in GB). A value of `0` disables caching."
msgstr "`--mm-processor-cache-gb` 设置多模态处理器缓存的大小（以 GB 为单位）。值为 `0` 表示禁用缓存。"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/PaddleOCR-VL.md:180
msgid ""
"`--dtype float16` specifies the model dtype. On Atlas 300 inference "
"products, only `float16` is supported."
msgstr "`--dtype float16` 指定模型数据类型。在 Atlas 300 推理产品上，仅支持 `float16`。"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/PaddleOCR-VL.md:181
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"`--compilation-config '{\"cudagraph_mode\":\"FULL_DECODE_ONLY\"}'` "
"enables full decode graph compilation for improved performance. On Atlas "
"300 inference products, `fuse_norm_quant` in graph compilation is "
"disabled by default in `--additional_config`."
msgstr ""
"`--compilation-config '{\"cudagraph_mode\":\"FULL_DECODE_ONLY\"}'` 启用完整解码图编译以提升性能。在 Atlas 300 推理产品上，`--additional_config` 中默认禁用了图编译的 `fuse_norm_quant`。"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/PaddleOCR-VL.md:182
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"`--additional_config '{\"enable_cpu_binding\":true}'` enables CPU binding"
" to improve performance."
msgstr "`--additional_config '{\"enable_cpu_binding\":true}'` 启用 CPU 绑定以提升性能。"

