#: ../../source/tutorials/models/PaddleOCR-VL.md:367
msgid ""
"**Note**: The following configurations are validated in specific test "
"environments and are for reference only. The optimal configuration "
"depends on factors such as maximum input/output length, precision "
"requirements, and actual hardware specifications. It is recommended to "
"refer to Section 9.2 for tuning based on actual conditions."
